Description: This is a 2017 les paul custom special grey body from stratosphere guitar parts store completely empty as body and neck then filled with following upgrades: Stew mac premium wiring harness Cts split pots Custom brushed gold pickguard 59 dimarzio bridge and neck pu’s Tonepros locking stud bolts Aged aluminum nickel wraparound bridge Hipshot 18:1 tuners Sozo tone capacitor 8.5 daddario strings Playability: Locking studs even the bridgepiece angle for low action. Adjustable with wrench The sustain is very good and acoustically it is loud with 9’s or higher gauge strings Lightweight body, no neck dive the body is slightly thinner than a les paul and more comfortable with top cut out. The neck profile is fast playing this guitar feels solid and unlike super heavy les pauls can keep on your lap for longer periods of time or easier on shoulder when standing. Sound: the Dimarzio 59 pickups and natural resonance of guitar sounds great clean or with distortion. Note: the selector switch is set to be up for bridge and down for neck for personal preference. That can be turned around and retightened by removing pickguard. No visible marks on body. Fully functional. the original les paul special custom was 1k and not good looking. This guitar now looks amazing and sounds alot better with dimarzio pickups. Does not have case. Will bubble wrap and double box for full shipping protection
Title: Gibson Les Paul Custom Special Super Modded
